item.title: ESEB 2019 in Turku
item.description: ESEB 2019 I attended the European Society for Evolutionary Biology (ESEB) biennial conference in Turku, Finland. I talked about my master thesis that experimental evolution reveald that relationships between resouce competition and reproductive interference. Thank you to everyone who took the time to discuss with me.
